  "body": "## Problem\r\n\r\n1. The input component has a bug in its styles, the left padding is thinner than expected.\r\n2. The API shouldn't receive a `variant` property, instead it should receive:\r\n    - a `blur` boolean parameter to specify if the variant is blur.\r\n    - an `override-theme` property, to override the theme if required.\r\n  \r\n    and should use the system's theme by default.\r\n  \r\n\r\n\r\n## Implementation\r\n\r\nWe need to change the input's code and update the screen preview.\r\n",
